        <td valign="top" width="80%"><h3><font color="#800000">About
        Us </font></h3>
        <p>Calumet Bancorp, Inc. headquarted in Dolton, Illinois
        is the holding company of Calumet Federal Savings and
        Loan Association of Chicago. Founded in 1910, Calumet
        Federal operates a community-based savings and loan with
        full-service offices located in southeastern Cook County,
        with two offices in Chicago and three suburban locations,
        currently serving over 16,000 households. </p>
        <p>Calumet Federal offers a wide range of quality
        financial products and services to meet the needs of the
        communities it serves. The primary business objective is
        making residential home loans and assisting customers to
        save and to plan for their financial future. </p>
        <p>The common stock of Calumet Bancorp, Inc. trades under
        the symbol of CBCI on the NASDAQ National Market System. </p>
        </td>
